{"tid":449594,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"以為買到原來買錯iPhone8?　「成個office都笑緊肥仔」","createTime":"2017-10-27T10:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T10:57:14.000Z","uid":51904,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2e11fcf3465ec7e49640cdd6c52e9aa73a4a9b","tid":449594,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:19:50.000Z","msg":"萬眾期待的蘋果iPhone X已於今午3點開賣，不足15分鐘已火速售罄。有人成功以iRerserve預購到，有人以Apple Online Store購買到，更多人不停「F5」但終失敗而回。不過，蘋果已公布下一輪iRerserve時間為11月4日上午8時，各果迷可以再接再厲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone X開賣的一刻，相信很多果迷都不停「F5」刷新網頁，在各大討論區都有果迷分享買機經歷，有網民指「比（畀）錢嗰刻彈返出去」、亦有人成功進入買機頁面，但未有按下購買按鈕，「選機時，見到（送貨時間）5-6周，放棄了」。<br />\n<br />\n買到機固然開心，但是有人空歡喜收場，有網民在討論區分享，有同事成功買到iPhone，但收到銀行通知過數後才發現買錯型號，哭笑不得，「我隔離肥仔同事收到銀行sms先知買錯咗iPhone8，（他）慘叫左一嘢，成個office都笑緊肥仔」。"},{"pid":"1e05ad8542bd846ddaa1c05dcd9934bef0b085c1","tid":449594,"uid":20286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2d570d9e9fabbd07612922d9ad286623e0b20a","tid":449594,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c055fe3101c4c103f16f7c9a8bc8dc0ee6ccaa7","tid":449594,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f07b8f3fee2e07dc896721f156d2f77097f23d","tid":449594,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"[麵包打老豆]白痴肥仔iphone8當iphoneX 慘遭恥笑"},{"pid":"7cd202a63bc3c9893b046cc24205f4ac86c0163b","tid":449594,"uid":3232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"咁熟口熟面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}